title: Â added to spaces in SVGs in Atom on Windows
body:
#### Code Sample

```stata
sysuse auto
scatter price mpg, title("This has a space at end ")
scatter price mpg, title("This has no spaces at end")
```
#### Problem description

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15164633/45051270-add42080-b051-11e8-9297-a638f683f492.png)

I think this is a Hydrogen or maybe Atom core bug?

The svg's display fine in Chrome:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15164633/45051429-10c5b780-b052-11e8-86a0-02424cacd773.png)

It appears I can't add svg attachments, but below are the files
<details>
